{"tid":2128502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登神探召喚] 禮頓山豪宅女子吸毒跳樓案","createTime":"2020-07-28T04:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T07:23:34.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"826ee47ba61af07e66477df51577dfab2a2f9237","tid":2128502,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:24:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/502748/獨家-禮頓山27歲女墮樓亡-疑劏場大王同居女友-室內檢可卡因\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F502748%2F%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E7%A6%AE%E9%A0%93%E5%B1%B127%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%A1-%E7%96%91%E5%8A%8F%E5%A0%B4%E5%A4%A7%E7%8E%8B%E5%90%8C%E5%B1%85%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B-%E5%AE%A4%E5%85%A7%E6%AA%A2%E5%8F%AF%E5%8D%A1%E5%9B%A0&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=dbb04f4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/502748/獨家-禮頓山27歲女墮樓亡-疑劏場大王同居女友-室內檢可卡因</a><br />\n<br />\n跑馬地豪宅禮頓山昨晨一名27歲女子墮樓亡，警方入屋調查檢獲多包可卡因，拘捕單位內的58歲男住戶。《香港01》追查後有驚人發現，該名被捕男子是58歲「劏場大王」尹柏權，消息稱，他數月前力追27歲女室內設計師，近日女方已搬入上址一高層單位共赴同居，至昨早女事主被發現由高處墮下，倒臥6座平台，當場不治。警方循線索追查至樓上單位，破門入屋後發現尹在內，並在單位內檢獲約12.5克懷疑可卡因，遂以涉嫌販毒拘捕尹柏權，正追查女事主墮樓原因。案件列作販毒及有人從高處墮下跟進。　<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">至昨（26日）早9時許，警方接報禮頓山一名女子懷疑由高處墮下，倒臥上址6座平台，救護員到場，證實27歲何女當場死亡。警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查相信她從上址一單位的洗手間墮下，事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，警方破門後進入涉事單位調查，於單位的書房及主人房內，檢獲30多個透明膠袋，載有共重約12.5克懷疑可卡因、多個吸食工具，<strong><ins>以及有多達17萬元現鈔散落單位不同角落。</ins></strong>警員在單位內發現尹柏權，搜身後再檢獲一個疑曾載可卡因的透明膠袋，以涉嫌販毒將他拘捕。案件交由灣仔警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進。</span>"},{"pid":"1c266d6da7054b82e35d018c60868ff350543301","tid":2128502,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:25:39.000Z","msg":"以及有多達17萬元現鈔散落單位不同角落。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa40026dce68dd6f983e2c7d3a04cfa7a3ed8c0","tid":2128502,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"沒有可疑"},{"pid":"93d3537ae3bdfcce86996ad4aa9aac867c5bcef6","tid":2128502,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:27:24.000Z","msg":"炒燶？劏場大王尹柏權涉藏毒被捕 同居27歲女友禮頓山墮樓亡<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2128227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2128227</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5cc2cbac1d5f5cfad3f2cd3cdfabdc5dae11eaa5","tid":2128502,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:28:29.000Z","msg":"1. 12克白粉<br />\n2. 17萬現金散滿一地<br />\n3. 女仔去廁所跳樓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f9788b762404cf6537d728023d390dfb80b0d9","tid":2128502,"uid":78165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:29:25.000Z","msg":"揼落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aad3fd1bbe0144765bc3e9aa8305b3e43a13525","tid":2128502,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTg7p0CK_WQm4GG8tjlUkI0AJn6667nxUnfvw&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcTg7p0CK_WQm4GG8tjlUkI0AJn6667nxUnfvw%26usqp%3DCAU&h=116b28f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n禮頓山6座圖則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b418a1388b5e6e86ade20037b04d6f3c9c84b8a","tid":2128502,"uid":13468,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"1c266d6da7054b82e35d018c60868ff350543301","tid":2128502,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0